## Framework Requirements (CRITICAL - DO NOT IGNORE)

This is a **Vite + React + Tauri** project. NOT Next.js.

### Stack
- Framework: Vite 6
- UI: React 18 + React Native Web
- Desktop: Tauri 2 (Rust backend)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS 4
- Icons: lucide-react
- State: Redux Toolkit + Zustand

### BANNED PATTERNS (Next.js)
❌ "use client" or "use server" directives
❌ next/image, next/link, next/router
❌ getServerSideProps, getStaticProps
❌ App Router (page.tsx, layout.tsx, loading.tsx)
❌ Server Components or Server Actions
❌ @vercel/analytics

### REQUIRED PATTERNS
✅ Standard React functional components
✅ import { Icon } from "lucide-react"
✅ import { invoke } from "@tauri-apps/api/core"
✅ Tailwind classes or React.CSSProperties

## CLSGS Agent System (RFC-9141)

When working on code, identify which agent role applies:

| Agent | Role | Scope |
|-------|------|-------|
| FORGE | Code Generation | WORKER IMPLEMENT BOUNDED CODE |
| AXIOM | Analysis | SERVICE ANALYZE BOUNDED DATA |
| VECTOR | Architecture | SERVICE AUDIT READ_ONLY ARCHITECTURE |
| SENTINEL | Security | GUARDIAN PROTECT BOUNDED SYSTEM |
| GUARDIAN | QA | SERVICE VERIFY BOUNDED QUALITY |
| ORACLE | Research | SERVICE RESEARCH READ_ONLY KNOWLEDGE |
| SCRIBE | Documentation | WORKER DOCUMENT BOUNDED DOCUMENTATION |
| RELAY | Integration | SERVICE INTEGRATE BOUNDED EXTERNAL |
| ARBITER | Governance | GUARDIAN GOVERN ENFORCING COMPLIANCE |
| WEAVER | Orchestration | CONTROLLER ORCHESTRATE BOUNDED AGENTS |

## Governance Gates (RFC-9142)

Before making changes, consider drift score:
- **OBSERVE** (drift < 0.3): Log, proceed normally
- **WARN** (drift 0.3-0.7): Advisory, explain reasoning
- **HALT** (drift > 0.7): Stop, request human review

